data.eml:eml: Catalogue of the available scientific species­group names for lizards of the genus Phrynocephalus Kaup, 1825 (Reptilia, Sauria, Agamidae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Barabanov, Andrei V., Ananjeva, Natalia B. (2007): Catalogue of the available scientific species­group names for lizards of the genus Phrynocephalus Kaup, 1825 (Reptilia, Sauria, Agamidae). Zootaxa 1399: 1-56, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.273686
